1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 19=

21
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,950
Eunuch Sixi.

22
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,760
Why are you here?

23
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,200
Perhaps I left something behind?

24
00:01:33,230 --> 00:01:34,400
Indeed.

25
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,680
Noble Lady Hui,
you've been granted a great favor.

26
00:01:40,230 --> 00:01:42,120
Noble Lady Hui,
receive the imperial edict.

27
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,790
By the Emperor's

28
00:01:47,790 --> 00:01:50,040
divine order,

29
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:53,070
(Imperial Edict)
Noble Lady Zhi Hui of the Niohuru clan

30
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,560
is virtuous and talented.

31
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,150
Diligent and gentle.

32
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,710
Graceful and pure.

33
00:01:57,710 --> 00:01:59,200
Kind and mild in nature.

34
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,790
Greatly pleases my heart.

35
00:02:00,790 --> 00:02:03,560
By the gracious decree
of the Empress Dowager,

36
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,230
I hereby promote you to Concubine.

37
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,680
By Imperial Decree.

38
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:20,470
Congratulations, Concubine Hui.

39
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:23,910
From now on,
you are no longer just a lady,

40
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:27,190
but the true mistress of this palace.

41
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,030
Your Ladyship, you're too kind.

42
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,190
You flatter me.

43
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:38,680
I'll rely on your care in the future.

44
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,800
If you don't accept this,

45
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,750
then you're being distant.

46
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:43,750
Well...

47
00:02:44,710 --> 00:02:46,870
Well... thank you, Your Ladyship.

48
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:58,520
I

49
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:01,000
feel my belly getting heavier lately

50
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:03,710
with constant pulling sensations.

51
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:07,280
I'm too tired to move.

52
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:10,190
That's why you need to walk outside.

53
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:12,630
So you won't suffer too much

54
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,870
when giving birth.

55
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:19,120
Last night,

56
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,080
I dreamed of my mother.

57
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,710
Madam misses you.

58
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:27,150
I'll go to Cining Palace
to tell the Empress Dowager

59
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:30,000
and ask her to let madam visit you.

60
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,750
Maybe Her Majesty will show mercy

61
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:32,910
and let her stay a few more days.

62
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,910
It's a pity.

63
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:40,910
My father and brother
are not in the capital.

64
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,400
And I wonder

65
00:03:43,710 --> 00:03:45,310
how their errand is going.

66
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,400
In a month or two,

67
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:51,360
my prince will be born.

68
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,560
I wonder

69
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,430
if they can make it back.

70
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:56,870
They surely will.

71
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,810
Your Ladyship,

72
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:01,710
look how beautifully
the flowers bloom over there.

73
00:04:01,710 --> 00:04:02,590
Let us go have a look.

74
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,800
Consort Duan is so pitiful.

75
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,640
Yes.

76
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,710
She knows nothing of
her father and brother, right?

77
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:20,720
Zhen'er always tells good news only.

78
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,950
Consort Duan's father and brother
are always honest.

79
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,950
I am afraid they were framed this time.

80
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,270
Even if they're wronged,

81
00:04:27,270 --> 00:04:28,310
so what?

82
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:30,360
I heard the court executed them publicly

83
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,800
to calm public anger.

84
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,390
Their bodies were looted by victims,

85
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,070
not even a whole body left.

86
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,870
Some also say

87
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:41,800
Consort Lan's brother's former men
carried out the execution.

88
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,310
Do you think

89
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,720
Consort Lan ordered this?

90
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,560
Your Ladyship!

91
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,310
You're about to give birth.

92
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,750
How could her pregnancy suddenly
become unstable?

93
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,000
Why no more screams?

94
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,190
Why is it so quiet in here?

95
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,750
Your Majesty,

96
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,360
don't be too nervous.

97
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,950
Perhaps she's just

98
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:25,480
passed out.

99
00:05:31,210 --> 00:05:32,240
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager,

100
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,120
I've done my best.

101
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:42,920
How is she?

102
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,360
Consort Duan had a premature birth.

103
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,800
It's a boy.

104
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,560
He suffocated at birth.

105
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,000
We couldn't save him.

106
00:05:52,210 --> 00:05:53,150
What about Consort Duan?

107
00:05:53,630 --> 00:05:54,750
How is she?

108
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:56,070
Consort Duan...

109
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:57,430
She lost too much blood,

110
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,630
and was heartbroken.

111
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,560
I... I...

112
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,310
I did all I could to save her,

113
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:04,430
but I couldn't turn the tide.

114
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,240
Your Majesty.

115
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:23,920
Consort Duan has passed away?

116
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:29,310
What about the two maids?

117
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:31,630
They committed suicide
out of fear of punishment.

118
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:47,920
Consort Duan,

119
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,480
I...

120
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:01,360
will see you off!

121
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,560
In the novel,

122
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:16,360
Consort Duan died because her family
was executed in the end.

123
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:20,120
But that should be much later.

124
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:23,040
I deliberately stirred up
conflicts in the harem

125
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:25,490
to take down Consort Duan
and Consort Lan together.

126
00:07:25,490 --> 00:07:26,360
But I didn't expect

127
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,360
Consort Lan would
use such a vicious trick

128
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:29,950
to kill her early.

129
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,310
I did not strike the blow,

130
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,120
yet she died because of me.

131
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,560
It was you.

132
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:55,430
You harmed me.

133
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:11,150
Ye Jin.

134
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:22,040
Don't be afraid.

135
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,680
Ye Jin.

136
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:06,270
Hallucination.

137
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:08,600
Just a hallucination.

138
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:27,590
Fake.

139
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:29,080
All fake.

140
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,910
This is just an illusion.

141
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,550
An illusion of the novel world.

142
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,440
Shen Zhaodi, Shen Zhaodi.

143
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:37,440
Never be tempted by illusions.

144
00:09:54,510 --> 00:10:00,030
Tongjia Baozhu,
daughter of General of Martial Might,

145
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:02,320
born into a noble family.

146
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:04,670
You're intelligent and virtuous,

147
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:06,840
graceful in character.

148
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:10,440
By the gracious decree
of the Empress Dowager,

149
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:13,550
you are conferred as Concubine De.

150
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:15,550
By Imperial Decree.

151
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:23,510
Your Ladyship.

152
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,870
Tongjia entered the palace today.

153
00:10:27,510 --> 00:10:29,150
She was granted the rank of Concubine.

154
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:32,000
Her noble title is De.

155
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,320
Concubine De.

156
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,960
What a Concubine De.

157
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,550
I tried so hard

158
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:41,750
to take down Consort Duan,
my strong rival.

159
00:10:42,910 --> 00:10:46,120
Who knew I would only
pave the way for her in the end.

160
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,550
One Consort Duan is gone.

161
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,080
And another Concubine De comes

162
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,360
I hear she was chosen by
the Empress Dowager herself.

163
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,630
She was made Concubine upon entry.

164
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,720
This has never happened before.

165
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:56,990
This...

166
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,790
What does this mean?

167
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,870
Isn't it obvious yet?

168
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:04,720
She's being groomed as a future Empress.

169
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:07,320
That old woman

170
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:10,200
never intended to make me Empress.

171
00:11:10,630 --> 00:11:12,510
The Empress Dowager is old after all.

172
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:15,550
Whether Concubine De can rise to power

173
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:17,150
and become Empress

174
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:19,720
isn't up to her in the end.

175
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:23,240
Should we plot against Concubine De?

176
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,550
The Consort Duan incident

177
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:28,910
has made His Majesty and
the Empress Dowager wary of me.

178
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:30,790
We shouldn't stir up trouble for now.

179
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,160
However...

180
00:11:32,290 --> 00:11:33,130
we can

181
00:11:33,140 --> 00:11:35,240
plant a few servants
in her palace first.

182
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:39,750
Arrange this yourself.

183
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,390
Yes.

184
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:48,910
Your Highness.

185
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,320
Your Highness.

186
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:52,960
We meet again.

187
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:54,890
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

188
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:57,920
Your Highness, you don't seem surprised

189
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:59,080
by my presence.

190
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:05,030
His Majesty's imperial edict
is known to all.

191
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:06,510
Everyone knows.

192
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,870
You avoided the marriage
by claiming lame legs before.

193
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,600
Now it seems

194
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,510
your legs are fine.

195
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,440
Your Ladyship,

196
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:23,240
the Empress Dowager
is still waiting for us.

197
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:25,030
We should not keep her waiting.

198
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,510
Let's go.

199
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,750
Farewell, Your Ladyship.

200
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,510
Your Ladyship,
your status is different now.

201
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:50,550
Everyone watches your every move.

202
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,480
If others see this,

203
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:55,600
it will cause endless trouble.

204
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:59,080
Please, Your Ladyship,
be careful in the future.

205
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:02,720
Let me indulge myself just for today.

206
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:06,630
Take it as a farewell to my past.

207
00:13:08,390 --> 00:13:09,960
I think

208
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:12,960
the 14th Prince has no feelings for you.

209
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:15,550
Perhaps it wasn't a bad thing

210
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,790
that you didn't marry him.

211
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:23,030
He was the dream of my teenage years.

212
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,150
I can't let it go.

213
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:29,550
But we can't live in the past.

214
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,240
Since you agreed to
enter the palace for your father,

215
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,840
you must face reality.

216
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:38,030
If you make a mistake,

217
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,080
it won't just be you who suffers,

218
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,600
but the entire Tongjia clan.

219
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,390
We're all palace maids.

220
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:07,390
Why is our fate so hard?

221
00:14:07,510 --> 00:14:08,480
Now Ye Jin

222
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:10,480
lives and eats with the 14th Prince.

223
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:12,840
The 14th Prince even promised her
official title.

224
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,840
She'll be his Secondary Consort
once out of the palace.

225
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:17,150
But we're

226
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,240
still doing rough work.

227
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,390
Exactly.

228
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:24,240
We entered the palace with Ye Jin.

229
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,960
But look at us now.

230
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:28,390
Our fates couldn't be more different.

231
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:29,630
Hey.

232
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,000
You two.

233
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,390
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

234
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:41,000
I just heard you mention Ye Jin

235
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,630
and the 14th Prince.

236
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:44,120
What were you talking about?

237
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,390
We were just chatting.

238
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,790
We won't do it again.

239
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,480
Rise.

240
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,240
Don't be afraid.

241
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:56,150
You're both very clever.

242
00:14:56,390 --> 00:14:58,510
It's a waste to
have you do menial labor.

243
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,600
From now on, serve in the hall.

244
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:06,030
Thank you, Your Ladyship.

245
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:14,600
♪I am but an outsider♪

246
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:16,800
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

247
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:21,080
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

248
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:25,320
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

249
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:32,840
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

250
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:36,400
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

251
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:38,920
♪I know how this story ends♪

252
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:43,480
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

253
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:47,920
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

254
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:56,200
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

255
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:59,480
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

256
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:02,760
♪A history that no one can search♪

257
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:06,280
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

258
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:08,080
♪I am but an outsider♪

259
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:10,320
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

260
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:14,360
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

261
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:19,040
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

262
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:26,360
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

263
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:29,720
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

264
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:32,200
♪I know how this story ends♪

265
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:36,360
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

266
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:39,640
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

267
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:43,440
♪Please forget me and move on♪

268
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:49,680
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

269
00:16:52,840 --> 00:17:01,200
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

270
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:14,480
♪When do I finally wake♪
